  58:Utilities/lpm/tiny_lpm/stm32_lpm.c ****  *        UTIL_LPM_EXIT_CRITICAL_SECTION. In general, the request to enter the
  59:Utilities/lpm/tiny_lpm/stm32_lpm.c ****  *        low power mode is already done under a critical section and 
  60:Utilities/lpm/tiny_lpm/stm32_lpm.c ****  *        nesting it is useless (in specific implementations not even possible). 
